[[include :scp-wiki:info:start]]
**SCP-9733-D:** Alex Thorley Figures Out Staplers
by [[*user BlazingPie]]

//That's the least you could give them.//

[[include :scp-wiki:component:ratio-bar pie=--]]

[[include :scp-wiki:info:end]]

